<td class="postcell">
<div>
    <div class="post-text" itemprop="description">
        <p>I want to merge an audio file (.wav or .au format) with a video file (.mp4 format).</p>

<p>Please suggest me a open-source utility to achieve this. I want to merge these file to new .mp4 video file. An ffmpeg command would be very welcome.</p>

    </div>
